Model.Text: One day, you suddenly receive an invitation to a mysterious banquet.
The sender is addressed to a Jake Stinchy, a name which is completely unfamiliar to you.
Just as you think you'll be rejecting the invitation, an intoxicating scent wafts up from the parchment.
You begin to feel light, as if your body is floating.
It's a wonderful feeling...

When you come to, you've completely lost track of time. 

What's more, you seem to have accepted the invitation, finding yourself inside of a grand mansion.
Suddenly, the mansion's towering front doors creak open, and dozens of new guests all holding the same invitation make their way inside.
It seems you're not the only one confused here...
Welcome all of you to my humble abode. Shall we together enjoy a splendid evening?
I am your host, Jack Stinchy.
As for this mask, it's...
Well it's just something of a style choice. Don't pay it any mind.
I've invited you all here tonight so that you may help me complete something of a task. A teensy, tiny little task.
You see I've misplaced something of great importance to me somewhere in this mansion, and I can't seem to find it for the life of me...
Now hold on, there was nothing written on my invitation! I never agreed to come here!
I... I don't even know how I ended up here! I want to go home!
Th-The door's locked!?
What is the meaning of this!? Let us go, now!

Ohoho~ Don't worry, don't worry~
As long as you find what I've lost, then you can all go home.
What do you want us to look for, anyway?
Once you find everything, and return it to me, your question shall be answered.
And what if we can't find it?
I hope you all have a eventful night.
You think if we don't find it... we'll be stuck here forever...?
